com.gembox.spreadsheet

Class DynamicFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gembox.spreadsheet.Filter
      • com.gembox.spreadsheet.DynamicFilter

  • public final class DynamicFilter
extends Filter
    Represents a dynamic filter criteria that can change, either with the data itself (e.g., "above average") or with the current system date (e.g., show values for "today").
    See Also:
    AutoFilter for examples which show various ways to specify and apply a filter to a range of cells, Excel AutoFiltering example
